==Description==
The '''Draco Plate''' is a type of [[Underground|Underground Item]].

==Details==
The Draco Plate has a value of 100 [[Gems|Dragon Gems]] {{Gem|Dragon}} when sold. It can also be traded in Daily Deals.

==Acquisition==
Draco Plates can be found in the [[Underground]], traded for with the [[Berry Master|Hoenn Berry Master]], and as Loot in [[Dungeons]].

